{"tid":1045750,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"揸車有冇聽過/經歷啲咩靈異嘢？","createTime":"2019-03-03T18:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T11:25:43.000Z","uid":182127,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"df821252eb32b686690ff4f732632a36fc5ac3a8","tid":1045750,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T18:20:40.000Z","msg":"如題！<br />\n我自己就冇。<br />\n開哩個post係因為早幾日個fd講開話摩星嶺嗰度深夜好猛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以想睇下大家有乜經歷同聽過啲乜？"},{"pid":"147e07517a3225cbd49698fbe061d255e2d9228b","tid":1045750,"uid":103540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T18:26:43.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8173e343ed40828fae00a8d8a70e9608d2ae0522","tid":1045750,"uid":196924,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T00:15:04.000Z","msg":"啲人話有車就會有女<br />\n但係我完全見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪我鬼奄眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a5728d26a2681b80b8553c127aec300428c185","tid":1045750,"uid":164932,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T00:27:25.000Z","msg":"試過盂蘭節果晚車完女朋友返屋企<br />\n佢拎左個豆腐花比我係車食<br />\n因為格黎係垃圾房 我食完順手一下dum過去<br />\n屌 點知中左個化寶盆<br />\n之後就著車走 一走果時 條路係轉右灣<br />\n果刻即刻個人冇左意識 直到撞左落條欄度先有返意識<br />\n好肯定自己冇暈 但著車到撞車期間冇左記憶 過程大約十幾秒<br />\n好似果識冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係賠死我<br />\n但果次都好甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637bab812106dee53336c0cb5b585c4182f6fc13","tid":1045750,"uid":38331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:13:16.000Z","msg":"摩星嶺凌晨時分自己上過去<br />\n除左半路有間公廁好撚恐怖之外上到頂都冇咩<br />\n<br />\n反而凌晨去新娘潭就真係慌慌地<br />\n時運高到出入都未見過人同車   得d牛"},{"pid":"1b22ff83bd82723afbd518c895d25f01dda58b45","tid":1045750,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68a5728d26a2681b80b8553